de.jcommandlineparser
Class OptionBuilder

java.lang.Object
  de.jcommandlineparser.OptionBuilder

public class OptionBuilder
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides static factory methods for creating program options.
Typical use would be like this:

OptionBuilder.buildNewOption("funf", 'f');
OptionBuilder.setRequired(); // only if option is required.
OptionBuilder.setDescription("description");
IntegerOption funfOption = OptionBuilder.getNewIntegerOption();

Author:
bananenkasper
